---

<section id="equipo" class="w-full bg-white py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-4">
        Nuestro <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent" style="font-family: var(--font-secondary)">equipo</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Conoce a los tiburones que lideran cada estrategia con precisión y ferocidad.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Tiburón 1 - Lopera -->
      <div class="group relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-blue-50 border-2 border-purple-200 hover:border-purple-600 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-40 h-40 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 mb-6 rounded-full bg-white p-4 shadow-lg group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/images/tiburones/lopera.png" 
              alt="Lopera Tiburón" 
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Lopera</h3>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-4">Director Creativo</p>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic">
            "La creatividad sin estrategia es arte. La estrategia sin creatividad es aburrida. Nosotros dominamos ambas."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tiburón 2 - Mauro -->
      <div class="group relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-purple-50 border-2 border-blue-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-40 h-40 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 mb-6 rounded-full bg-white p-4 shadow-lg group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/images/tiburones/mauro.png" 
              alt="Mauro Tiburón" 
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Mauro</h3>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600 mb-4">Diseñador Grafico</p>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic">
            "Los datos no mienten. Las estrategias mediocres sí. Por eso siempre vamos por más."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tiburón 3 - Community Manager -->
      <div class="group relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 border-2 border-green-200 hover:border-green-600 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-40 h-40 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 mb-6 rounded-full bg-white p-4 shadow-lg group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/images/tiburones/cm.png" 
              alt="Community Manager Tiburón" 
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Community Manager</h3>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-green-600 mb-4">Community Manager</p>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic">
            "Cada interacción cuenta. Cada comunidad importa. Construimos conexiones que transforman."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tiburón 4 - Camila -->
      <div class="group relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-rose-50 border-2 border-pink-200 hover:border-pink-600 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-40 h-40 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 mb-6 rounded-full bg-white p-4 shadow-lg group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/images/tiburones/kami.png" 
              alt="Camila Tiburón" 
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Camila</h3>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-pink-600 mb-4">Editora</p>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic">
            "Cada frame cuenta una historia. Cada corte define la emoción. Editamos con pasión y precisión."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tiburón 5 - Villa -->
      <div class="group relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-amber-50 border-2 border-orange-200 hover:border-orange-600 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-40 h-40 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 mb-6 rounded-full bg-white p-4 shadow-lg group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/images/tiburones/villa.png" 
              alt="Villa Tiburón" 
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Villa</h3>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-orange-600 mb-4">Filmaker</p>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic">
            "Capturamos momentos. Creamos emociones. Cada proyecto es una obra maestra en movimiento."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tiburón 6 - Steven -->
      <div class="group relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-violet-50 border-2 border-indigo-200 hover:border-indigo-600 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-40 h-40 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 mb-6 rounded-full bg-white p-4 shadow-lg group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/images/tiburones/ladino.png" 
              alt="Steven Tiburón" 
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Steven</h3>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-600 mb-4">Estratega Digital</p>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic">
            "La estrategia es el mapa. La ejecución es el territorio. Navegamos ambos con maestría."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

